WEBVTT

00:03:28.812 --> 00:03:31.552
He's at home now with my two kids,

00:03:31.576 --> 00:03:34.266
and I have another one
that's growing in here.

00:03:34.869 --> 00:03:40.044
(Applause)

00:03:40.594 --> 00:03:43.939
When I'm working,
I call him every two hours,

00:03:43.963 --> 00:03:47.753
and he knows if he doesn't hear from me,

00:03:47.777 --> 00:03:49.204
he should call my contact,

00:03:49.228 --> 00:03:52.390
the one who gives me access to the story,

00:03:52.414 --> 00:03:55.004
which is the one who I trust.

00:03:57.105 --> 00:03:59.130
One of the times in Gaza,

00:03:59.154 --> 00:04:04.093
during the kidnapping
of the British journalist Alan Johnston,